cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">同时，我县致力于引进大连成达、香港智达集团、周黑鸭、瑞祥等畜产品加工企业，支持其建设规模化、标准化养殖基地，建立健全&ldquo;龙头企业<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">+</span>基地<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">+</span>农户&rdquo;的模式，协调企业与养殖户建立风险共担、利益均沾的一体化联结机制，助推我县生猪、水禽、奶业、蛋禽业实现跨越发展。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1383','6','陶满玲、童年','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-03-12/9d923470598ef44ada5056e8487459c1.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">参观井冈山革命博物馆<br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8</span>日至<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">10</span>日，县四大家机关女干部赴江西井冈山革命根据地开展学习教育活动。县政协主席葛婷、县人大副主任戴书萍、县政协副主席严嘉芬参加活动。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">女干部们先后参观了毛泽东同志旧居、黄洋界、中国红军第四军医院旧址、井冈山革命烈士陵园、井冈山革命博物馆等地，踏着先烈们的足迹，一路追思先辈们的丰功伟绩。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">在小井红四军医院旧址，讲解员描述了当年红军在条件极度艰苦、缺医少药的境况下，无私无畏、精诚团结、共度时艰的可歌可泣事迹，不少同志流下了感动的泪水。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">井冈山革命博物馆里，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3000</span>多件馆藏品忠实记载了红军战斗的峥嵘岁月，大家认真聆听着一个个催人泪下、传奇而又感人英雄事迹，亲眼目睹着一件件陈列实物，不仅心灵受到启迪，思想受到教育，而且深感党的伟大，人民江山的来之不易。在井冈山革命烈士陵园，女干部们还集体敬献了花圈，鞠躬默哀，重温入党誓词。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">县政协主席葛婷说，今年是我党十八大召开之年，组织大家重走井冈山革命之路，学习井冈山精神，就是要大家坚定跟党走的信念，加强依靠群众、从群众中来到群众中去的工作作风，树立星星之火可以燎原、革命和改革必将从胜利走向胜利的信心。她要求女干部结合井冈精神，结合省、市、县委<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&ldquo;</span>喜迎十八大、争创新业绩<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&rdquo;</span>主题实践活动，以更饱满的精神、更有力的举措、更务实的作风，立足岗位、敬业乐业，以更优异的工作业绩，向党的十八大献礼！<br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-03-12/f219c9c39b2ef22d85c287f9289a072b.jpg\\\\\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">敬献花圈</span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1384','6','周艳','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><st1:chsdate w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" day=\\\\\"12\\\\\" month=\\\\\"3\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2012\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>日</st1:chsdate>，从嘉鱼县旅游局传来喜讯，经市乡村休闲游星级评定委员会<span style=\\\\\"color: black\\\\\">评定</span>，我县逸湖农庄、湾湖农庄和丁家曾农庄等<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>家农家乐被正式评定为三星级农家乐，这是我县首批获评的三星级农家乐。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">据悉，自</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">县委、县政府去年出台《关于鼓励和扶持农家乐旅游的意见》以来，我县农家乐蓬勃发展，</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">农家乐的经营规模、结构体系、参与人数得到了不断提升壮大</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">。目前，全县各类规模农家乐已达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">90</span>余家，就地就近带动近千人就业。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">在支持农家乐旅游发展中，我县对照农家乐星级划分与评定标准，规范和引导农家乐旅游经营行为，对申报扶持资金的农家乐旅游经营户，以及符合扶持条件并积极参加创业培训、接受行业指导的农家乐经营业主，给予每户<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>万元的资金补贴，超过<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>万元的小额担保贴息贷款，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>年内免收属于管理类、登记类、证照类的各项行政事业性收费等优惠政策。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">据县旅游局有关负责人介绍，今年是我县&ldquo;乡村旅游发展年&rdquo;，我县将依托丰富的旅游资源，大力发展乡村旅游，重点扶持和规范一批农家乐经营户，支持一批有特色、基础好、前景好的农家乐做大做强，优化和调整农村产业结构，促进农村劳动力转移就业，开辟农民增收致富的新渠道，使&ldquo;农家乐&rdquo;建设成为新农村靓丽风景线和生态旅游经济新亮点。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"> <o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1385','6','熊铁山','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-03-13/9648074f03f529e0c3aa9f0d4bc6a657.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n活动现场<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&ldquo;现在食品添加剂到处都是，如果买了不健康的食品，肯定会对身体造成伤害。我们普通人怎样鉴别食品是否健康安全？&rdquo;<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">13</span>日，嘉鱼县质监局在电信广场举办了食品安全宣传活动，许多市民前来咨询。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&ldquo;买食品要买原色食品，不要买那些颜色特别鲜亮的，卖相特别好的，比如买鸡爪子就不要挑那些泡得白白的、鼓起来的，那很可能就是用双氧水泡的。&rdquo;县质监局食品监管股股长李永祥详细的给前来咨询的群众解说，并鼓励大家遇到不法商户，应及时向质监局稽查分局举报，电话号码是<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6358229</span>。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">活动现场设置了检测服务台、咨询服务台、投诉举报台。许多群众前来咨询食品安全等方面的知识，工作人员有问必答，耐心讲解，并现场发放宣传资料<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1000</span>余份，向市民普及<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">QS</span>认证、食品添加剂、危害健康的四种食品添加剂、有机食品、绿色食品等方面的知识。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">据悉，该局还将开展食品安全宣传进机关、进企业、进学校、进社区等一系列活动，以提高全社会的食品安全意识，营造人人重视食品安全的良好社会氛围。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1386','6','熊铁山','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-03-15/b4cc68524bcb4cdd016dd67a2df59137.jpg\\\\\" alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" /><br />\r\n参观潘家湾村党员群众服务中心<br />\r\n</span></font></div>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">3</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">14</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，孝感市委组织部领导赴嘉鱼县参观考察农村党员群众服务中心建设工作。咸宁市委组织部副部长郭扬城，县委副书记李国光，县委常委、组织部长袁秋明陪同考察。</span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">考察组一行先后参观了官桥八组和潘家湾镇潘家湾村、苍梧岭村。看到各村都建起了党员群众服务中心，阅览室、书画室、活动室等一应俱全，并定期开展各种宣传教育活动，考察团对此赞不绝口。考察团负责人表示，嘉鱼经济发展迅速、基层党组织建设坚实、群众服务体系完善，非常值得孝感市各县市区学习借鉴。</span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">李国光对孝感市考察团的到来表示热烈欢迎，他希望孝感市和嘉鱼县之间继续加强交流与合作，共同学习，相互借鉴，实现优势互补，共同推动两地经济社会又好又快发展。</span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">据了解，潘家湾村现有人口</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">4699</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">人，村民小组</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">7</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个，党员</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">94</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">人。该村严格按照&ldquo;五务合一&rdquo;的要求，加强党员群众服务中心建设，新建了多功能会议室、电教室、卫生室、便民服务室、农家书屋等，实现了&ldquo;进中心家、办万家事&rdquo;目标，真正把党员群众服务中心建成了排忧解难的窗口、联系群众的桥梁、凝聚人心的家园。苍悟岭村现有人口</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">3226</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">人，村民小组</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">5</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个，党员</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">75</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">人。近年来，该村不断加强村级党组织建设，进一步公开和民主议事制度，提高了乡风文明程度。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2011</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年被省委、省政府授予省级&ldquo;文明村&rdquo;称号。</span></font></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-03-15/bd44c0f5bd876cbee7fe188d236c0566.jpg\\\\\" alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" /><br />\r\n参观官桥八组展厅</span></font></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1387','6','周艳、沈阳','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-03-15/866ca02be1470287faf91c5c180805aa.jpg\\\\\" alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" /><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体;\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px;\\\\\">龙潭大道施工现场</span></span></div>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&ldquo;前两天才听说这条路今年要维修，没想到这么快就动工了啊！&rdquo;<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">14</span>日，目睹嘉鱼县龙潭大道改造工程正式启动，北门湖居民纷纷拍手称快。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"> </span></font></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">记者在现场看到，龙潭大道部分路段已经设置了围挡和交通警示标识<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">,</span>施工人员也已进驻现场<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">,</span>挖掘机正在清理原有破损的路面，工人们忙着维持现场秩序，提醒过往车辆和行人注意通行安全。</font></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&ldquo;等前期修复、平整、养护等基础性工作完成了，还要进行刷黑呢！&rdquo;在施工现场协调指挥的骆师傅告诉记者，现阶段主要是对已破损路面进行进一步破除和碾压，然后重新铺设混凝土，预计今年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7</span>月底前完成改造。</font></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm;\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">据县住建局局长尹彬生介绍，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2012</span>年，我县预计投资<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2723</span>万元用于城区市政建设，并将以城区道路改造为突破口，着力提高城区道路档次，推动城市路网结构进一步完善。主要包括：北街、北门路、青山路、岳公路路面维修工程、通江路整体改造工程；龙潭大道、殷家坡路、岳公路、通湖路、龙潭湾路刷黑工程，凤凰路改造刷黑工程、东岳北路及延伸段刷黑工程；东岳北路及延伸段、岳公路、龙潭大道、通湖路、凤凰路人行道更换站石及拉丝板工程。</font></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm;\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1388','6','熊铁山','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-03-15/7d2ba9828190baa0e90a2aa331976fcd.jpg\\\\\" alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" /><br />\r\n接受投诉<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&ldquo;我要投诉蜂窝煤生产者，你们受不受理&rdquo;，说完这句话，家住嘉鱼县梁家山社区的张守洪老人拿出两个蜂窝煤和一把尺子，现场为大家测量了起来，&ldquo;你们看，以前的煤直径是<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">115</span>毫米，高度是<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">75</span>毫米，现在的煤直径是<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">110</span>毫米、高度是<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">70</span>毫米，明显不合格。国家对蜂窝煤肯定有一个统一标准，希望工商部门管一下。&rdquo;这是记者在中百超市<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3.15</span>活动现场咨询台前看到的一幕。</font></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">据介绍，今年的<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3&middot;15</span>纪念活动由县工商局和县消费者协会主办，县烟草局、农业局、畜牧局等十多个部门共同承办，共设<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">10</span>个分会场。活动当天，全县工商系统所有工作人员都走上街头，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&ldquo;</span>零距离<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&rdquo;</span>为群众维权，发放宣传材料<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4000</span>多份，接受群众咨询<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">200</span>多人次。此外还公开销毁假烟<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2800</span>条、假饮料<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">300</span>件、假酒<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">100</span>件、过期失效食品<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">500</span>件等假冒伪劣产品。</font></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&ldquo;今年，市民反映的问题主要集中在家装质量、家用电器、假冒伪劣商品等问题，我们将对市民举报的案件一一进行记录和调查&rdquo;县工商局局长李河生说，&ldquo;一年一度的<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3.15</span>纪念日是工商部门消保维权的一个缩影，也是一个起点。由此开始，维权工作将一步步卓有成效地开展下去。&rdquo;</font></span></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-03-15/8b5a95b1626091c72d162f1f3cd73c57.jpg\\\\\" alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" /><br />\r\n讲授如何辨别假烟</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1389','6','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-03-15/d00ed70b95736cc7e132633e490e8b4d.jpg\\\\\" alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" /><br />\r\n会议现场<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">15</span>日，记者从全县组织系统&ldquo;一迎双创&rdquo;主题活动推进会上获悉，我县将深入开展&ldquo;迎接党的十八大，争当&lsquo;三服务&rsquo;优秀标兵、争创&lsquo;两满意&rsquo;模范部门&rdquo;活动，力图通过丰富的活动内容，引导各级组织部门和广大组工干部加强党性修养，提高业务能力，改进工作作风。</font></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">会议要求，全县各级组织部门和广大组工干部开展党性标准大讨论，进一步明确组工干部讲党性的具体标准和要求。开展业务知识大宣讲，将中共党史、党章、组工业务、干部选拔任用条例等纳入学习重点，通过以会代训、以老带新、编印学习资料等形式，对全县组工人事干部进行组织工作业务知识的重点培训，提升组工干部的能力素质。深入基层大走访，开展&ldquo;五访问计&rdquo;活动，即访村&ldquo;两委&rdquo;成员，问壮大村级集体经济建议；访基层党员群众代表，问基层组织建设措施；访致富示范户，问创业致富办法；访各类人才，问人才强县路子；访生活困难群众，问脱贫致富难点。</font></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">县委常委、组织部长袁秋明强调，今年是党的十八大、省委第十次党代会的召开之年，中组部确定的&ldquo;基层组织建设年&rdquo;，省委、省政府&ldquo;重大项目建设年&rdquo;。面对非常之年，组织工作要求高、任务重、责任大，各级组工干部务必紧绷思想之弦，要以强烈的政治责任感和饱满的精神状态投入到工作中去。</font></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">袁秋明要求，各级组织部门务必要集中力量重点攻坚，抓好活动开展、人才培养、履职培训、满意度调查等工作。同时要创新举措，在抓落实上讲究方法、下足功夫；要坚持统筹兼顾，把握工作规律，注重以良好的工作机制、以务实的工作精神、以科学的方法路径、以积极的创新精神推动落实，争创嘉鱼组织工作的品牌。<br />\r\n</font></span></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-03-15/288b0f1b4ecde6a650692ff74a89fc77.jpg\\\\\" alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" /><br />\r\n会议现场</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center;\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1390','8','县政协','嘉鱼政务网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">为展现嘉鱼名人风采，扩大嘉鱼知名度，激励嘉鱼人建功立业，经县委同意，县政协文史委承办拟编辑出版《嘉鱼名人》。为确保嘉鱼名人信息采集和编撰工作顺利进行，为此向县直各单位、各镇、社会各界诚征名人信息，特制定本方案。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24.1pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">一、征集信息的名人范围</span></font></b></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1900</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年以前出生的嘉鱼籍名人信息原则上以</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1993</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年版《嘉鱼县志》上所载人物为据。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1900</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年以后出生的嘉鱼籍或主要工作在嘉鱼的现代各界名人，要求如下：</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">、政界：职务在副厅级以上；</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">、军界：职务在副师职以上；</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">3</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">、商界：个人资产在</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">8000</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万以上；或大中型企业主要负责人；</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">4</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">、学术界：获博士学位、教授或相当职称、博导职称、国家级荣誉；</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">5</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">、艺术界：获国家级荣誉并产生影响；</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">6</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">、其他人士：要求知名，对社会有较大影响。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">此次征集的信息供编撰《嘉鱼名人》作参考，入选人物由《嘉鱼名人》编委会根据成书需要从以上范围鳞选优秀代表确定。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24.1pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">二、方法步骤</span></font></b></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">、组织发动。在县政协工作会议上进行安排部署；在嘉鱼网公告。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">、搜集信息。县直各口、各镇要求</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2012</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">4</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">10</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">前将信息采集表反馈县政协文史委。网上名人信息征集放宽时限至</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2012</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">5</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">31</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">3</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">、确定人选。《嘉鱼名人》编辑部对各单位提供的名人线索进行汇总整理，初步筛选，并向有关单位反馈。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">4</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">、征集文稿。安排专人向嘉鱼名人及其所在单位征集文稿素材和照片。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">5</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">、文稿整理。本书编辑与嘉鱼名人双向沟通协作。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">6</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">、个人校核。将编辑好的文稿反馈收录的嘉鱼名人本人，校核无误后签字确认。本人无法校核的可由委托人代替。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24.1pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">三、资料管理</span></font></b></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">对于征集到的信息、稿件，嘉鱼县政协文史委将按照工作程序和科学方法进行登记、编号、分类、审读、整理、存档。对于原稿、函电、日记、图书和影像资料，在征得名人本人或委托人同意的前提下，妥为保管，使用完后根据情况要求返还的，我们一律返还。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24.1pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">四、联络方式</span></font></b></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">来稿、来信请寄：湖北省嘉鱼县政协文史委，邮编</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">437200</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">，李青山收。</span></font><