g: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 黑体; color: black; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">第五条</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; color: black; font-size: 14pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">&nbsp; </font></span></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">申请气象灾害应急准备工作认证的单位，须具备以下条件：</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">（一）建立气象灾害警报点或气象信息服务站，在灾害性天气影响期间有可以</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; color: black; font-size: 14pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">24</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">小时值班的工作场所；</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">（二）乡镇（街道）有一名负责人分管气象灾害防御工作，有一名或一名以上的气象协理员；气象灾害防御重点单位有分管领导和一名气象信息联络员，负责灾害性天气应急工作；</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">（三）有气象灾害应急处置预案；有安全的避难场所，可在灾害性天气发生时，安置转移人员；</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 