d; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 1.98\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">6</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">、完成县委、县政府交办的其他事项（<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>分）。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 35.15pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（三）银行业金融机构（<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">100</span>分）。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">、贷款净增额（<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">50</span>分）。净增额在全县金融机构中排名第一名得<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">50</span>分，每后退一名减<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>分。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">、贷款增长幅度</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">（<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>分）。增幅最大者得<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>分，其他单位按</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">与最高者的</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">比例得分</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">、增量贷存比（<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>分）。增量部分贷存比最高者得<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>分，其他单位按与最高者的比例得分。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">4</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">、新增<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">A</span>级信用企业（<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">10</span>分）。增幅达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">30%</span>以上得<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">10</span>分，增幅在<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">30%</span>以下按比率计分。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">、创新信贷机制、信贷产品，满足市场主体多元化的信贷需求（<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>分）。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">6</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">、不良贷款占比同比下降（<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>分）。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">7</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">、完成县委、县政府交办的其他事项（<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>分）。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">三、组织实施<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（一）考核工作由县政府办公室负责，有关部门配合。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（二）考核对象于次年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">10</span>日前向县政府办公室上报各基本内容信息资料，并对所报信息资料的真实性负责，一经发现有提供虚假信息的，取消其评奖资格。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（三）县政府办公室会同有关职能部门对县人民银行、县银监办和其他银行业金融机构进行考核。根据性质不同将考核内容分定量指标和定性指标。定量指标考核由各被考核单位提供材料，经有关部门认定后作为计分依据；定性指标由考核组各成员打分取平均分。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（四）考核结果经县政府分管领导审定后报县政府审批。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">四、奖励办法<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（一）</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">绩效考核奖励基金按每年不低<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">30</span>万元列入财政预算。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（二）</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">考核期内每引进一家全国性法人银行分支机构，对县人民银行和县银监办事处各另行奖励<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>万元；引进一家地方性商业银行分支机构，对县人民银行和县银监办事处各另行奖励<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4</span>万元。<b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（三）</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">县政府根据考核分值对所有考核对象进行排名，对总分前五名进行奖励<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">,</span>奖金发放办法另行安排。<b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（四）奖励资金主要奖给领导班子成员和其他有功人员。奖励受奖单位主要负责人奖金不得低于本单位所得奖金的<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">30%</span>，其他奖金由各单位自行安排。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（五）对新增贷款多，为全县经济社会发展做出突出贡献的单位，授予&ldquo;支持经济发展突出贡献奖&rdquo;称号，并给予专项奖励。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（六）对被考核单位全年目标任务完成情况予以通报，并抄送其上级主管部门。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 35pt; margin: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; font-